        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 3 at 5:09PM PDT until June 3 at 6:00PM PDT by NWS Las Vegas NV</headline>
        <description>SVRVEF

The National Weather Service in Las Vegas has issued a

* Severe Thunderstorm Warning for...
Northeastern Clark County in southern Nevada...

* Until 600 PM PDT.

* At 508 PM PDT, a severe thunderstorm was located over Logandale, or
7 miles north of Overton, moving north at 15 mph.

HAZARD...Quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Damage to vehicles is expected.

* Locations impacted include...
Overton, Moapa Town, Moapa Valley, and Logandale.

This includes Interstate 15 in Nevada between mile markers 91 and
101.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
